(1, 1, 'Google Cloud Platform: Growing Impact on Businesses in the Digital World', 'what-is-google-cloud-platform', 'The Google Cloud Platform (GCP) has emerged as a crucial aspect in shaping the digital landscape, offering scalable cloud solutions that power everything from enterprise-level businesses to innovative startups. In an era where digital transformation is beneficial and essential for survival and growth, GCP provides robust tools that foster innovation, scalability, and security. This blog covers the complexities of the Google Cloud Platform, highlighting its indispensable role, importance, and impact on today’s digital era.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/1_R63-rrt9Ei.jpg?updatedAt=1714998955590', 3, 'Why Google Cloud Platform is Essential for Your Business', ' Learn about the Google Cloud Platform and how it can help you grow your business with advanced security, scalability, and data-driven insights.', 'Google Cloud Platform, what is Google Cloud platform', 8, '2024-03-01', '2024-05-06 10:28:21', NULL),
(2, 1, 'Top Data Security Tools and Best Practices for Ensuring Your Online Safety', 'data-security-tools-and-practices', 'Securing your data is prudent and necessary in a digital realm filled with cyber threats. For small business owners and IT professionals, understanding the tools and practices that safeguard digital information is critical. This comprehensive guide will help you gain essential knowledge on data security, offering insights into the leading tools and best practices for fortifying your online presence.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/2_inFUeu4wV.jpg?updatedAt=1714998957470', 3, 'Data Security Guide: Top Tools & Practices for Online Safety', 'Learn the top data security tools and practices to protect your online presence. Understand everything from firewalls to encryption and beyond.', 'data security, what is data security, data security tools, data security practices', 1, '2024-03-02', '2024-05-06 10:30:32', NULL),
(3, 2, 'Explore India\'s Top 5 Business Management Degree Programs', '5-best-business-management-degree-programs', 'India\'s robust economic growth over the past few decades has created a crucial need for skilled business professionals. In response, numerous educational institutions have emerged, offering specialized business management degree programs to cater to this escalating demand.', 'Discover the top 5 business management degree programs in India that students and employers highly value. They aim to equip aspiring individuals with the necessary knowledge and skills to thrive in the constantly changing business environment.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/3_-UD2brbJ50.jpg?updatedAt=1714998963915', 2, 'India\'s Best 5 Business Management Degree Programs for 2024', 'Know India\'s top 5 business management degree programs for 2024. 1. Indian Institute of Management (IIM) • 2. Xavier School of Management (XLRI) and more.', 'Business Management Degree, Degree Programs, Degree Programs in India for 2024, Management Degree, Business Management', 7, '2024-03-03', '2024-05-06 10:32:25', NULL),
(4, 2, 'The Future of Digital Marketing: Courses You Can\'t-Miss in 2024', 'digital-marketing-courses-for-beginners', 'In an age where technology constantly transforms our ways of connecting and doing business, staying at the forefront of digital marketing is more important than ever. The digital marketing world of 2024 is set to introduce both new challenges and opportunities for marketers keen to establish their presence. ', 'No matter if you\'re a newcomer eager to enter this dynamic field or an experienced professional looking to enhance your digital expertise, the right training can pave the way to success. Here\'s a look ahead at the future of digital marketing through the essential courses aimed at boosting your skills.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/4_ltfFvOx9ta.jpg?updatedAt=1714998961905', 2, 'Top Digital Marketing Courses You Cannot Miss in 2024', 'Digital Marketing is one of the fastest-growing sectors in 2024. Dive into the field and upskill yourself with these popular digital marketing courses today!', 'digital marketing courses, digital marketing, digital marketing course', 2, '2024-03-05', '2024-05-06 10:34:29', NULL),
(5, 2, 'Consider These 5 Best Animation Courses in India for 2024', 'best-animation-courses', 'Animation is an ever-evolving and captivating domain that attracts individuals with creative flair and technological aptitude, all driven by a passion for storytelling. With its emerging entertainment industry and internationally acclaimed IT sector, India has become a prominent destination for animation education, fostering talent and driving innovation in this dynamic field.', 'As advanced technologies and digital platforms continue to rise, the demand for proficient animators in India has surged, emphasizing the importance of selecting the appropriate educational route. Let\'s explore some of India\'s top animation courses tailored for 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/5_-oG4ojtENH.jpg?updatedAt=1714998958318', 2, 'Explore the 5 Best Animation Courses in India for 2024', 'These are India\'s 5 best animation courses for 2024. 1. National Institute of Design (NID) • 2. Industrial Design Centre (IDC), IIT Bombay & more.', 'animation courses ,  National Institute of Design, NID, WWI, Industrial Design Centre, IDC', 6, '2024-03-05', '2024-05-06 10:37:48', NULL),
(6, 3, 'A Complete Guide to Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, and How to Prevent', 'cataract-surgery', 'Cataracts are a principal cause of vision impairment worldwide, affecting millions yearly. However, a comprehensive understanding of cataracts can significantly empower individuals, enabling them to proactively approach their visual health. ', 'We’ll unravel the mystery of cataracts, discover their common causes and symptoms, and discuss the crucial steps one can take toward their prevention. By gaining a deeper insight into these aspects, you can make informed decisions regarding your sight health and potentially minimize the impact of cataracts on your life.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/6_6ge1BFlfD-.jpg?updatedAt=1714998963843', 2, 'Everything About Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, Prevention', 'Are you facing cataracts? Read our guide on symptom recognition, when to opt for surgery, and post-surgery care for a smooth recovery and better eye health.', 'cataract surgery, cataract awareness, cataract causes, cataract symptoms, cataract prevention', 3, '2024-03-06', '2024-05-06 10:39:36', NULL),
(7, 4, 'Find Out the Benefits of Coworking Spaces for Digital Nomads', 'benefits-of-coworking-spaces-for-digital-nomads', 'In the past decade, coworking spaces have become increasingly popular, mirroring the growth of digital nomadism and remote work trends. These spaces function as collaborative hubs, resembling communal offices, and cater to freelancers, entrepreneurs, and startups alike. This blog analyzes the diverse advantages of coworking spaces, which are exceptionally appealing to digital nomads seeking flexibility while maintaining a professional environment.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/7_ROoYi4eEpG.jpg?updatedAt=1714998964737', 2, 'The Essential Benefits of Coworking Spaces for Digital Nomads', 'Explore the benefits that coworking spaces offer digital nomads, from stimulating creativity and innovation to encouraging a healthy work-life balance.', 'coworking spaces, spaces for modern business, digital nomads, advantages of coworking spaces', 5, '2024-03-07', '2024-05-06 10:41:48', NULL),
(8, 1, 'Stay Informed About These Cybersecurity Trends in 2024', 'key-cybersecurity-trends-for-2024', 'In our swiftly changing digital realm, the significance of cybersecurity is experiencing exponential growth. With technological advancements occurring at a blistering pace, businesses, IT professionals, and the general public must stay vigilant about cybersecurity trends. In 2024, significant shifts and challenges emerged, especially with the rise of Generative AI, Quantum Computing, and more sophisticated cybersecurity threats.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/8_VYNGgunmf.jpg?updatedAt=1714998961472', 3, 'Stay Informed About the Key Cybersecurity Trends for 2024', 'Discover the critical cybersecurity trends for 2024. 1. Artificial Intelligence (AI) & Machine Learning (ML) • 2. Internet of Things (IoT) Security, and more. ', 'cyber crimes, cybersecurity experts, cybersecurity degree, cybersecurity education', 4, '2024-03-08', '2024-05-06 10:44:11', NULL),
(9, 5, 'Home Security Cameras: How to Pick the Right One for Your Safety Needs', 'how-to-choose-the-right-home-security-system', 'Today, keeping our homes and loved ones safe is more important than ever, which means maintaining the proper security measures. Security cameras are vital for protecting our areas, but picking the best one with many options can take time.', 'Our guide makes it easy, giving you all the info you need to choose the right security camera system for your home. We\'ll help you figure out what you need and show you the newest features and tech in surveillance.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/9_jX8HgBWu4.jpg?updatedAt=1714998990861', 1, 'Looking for the best security camera for your home? From identifying your needs to understanding technical features, we\'ll help you make the right choice.', 'Looking for the best security camera for your home? From identifying your needs to understanding technical features, we\'ll help you make the right choice.', 'security camera for home, security camera system, safety', 4, '2024-03-09', '2024-05-06 10:50:34', NULL),
(10, 6, 'Next Level Gaming: Top 10 Online Games of 2024', 'online-games', 'In digital entertainment, online games have secured a paramount position, continually evolving to offer immersive experiences that captivate millions worldwide. The year 2024 is no exception, with many platforms catering to varied tastes and interests so that you can play online games with fun.', 'This article spotlights 10 online games that stand out for their innovation, community engagement, and overall gameplay quality. These games ensure everyone has a list of the best online games to explore.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/10_c7WmcoSRcN.jpg?updatedAt=1714999034583', 3, 'Top 10 Online Games You Need to Experience in 2024', 'These 10 online games will definitely elevate your gaming experience. 1. Roblox • 2. Minecraft • 3. Among Us • 4. Valorant • 5. Fortnite and more.', 'online games, play online games, online games to play, best online games', 2, '2024-03-10', '2024-05-06 10:52:26', NULL),
(11, 4, 'Call Center Trends Influencing Customer Experience in 2024', 'call-center-trends', 'In today\'s scenario, providing effective and efficient customer service is crucial for any brand\'s success. The call center sector has been pivotal in connecting businesses with customers and aiding brand expansion for many years. Nevertheless, meeting customer demands poses a flexible challenge due to the ever-changing market landscape. ', 'As companies aim to modernize their call center tactics, this article explores upcoming trends influencing customer service in 2024. From AI advancements to incorporating remote workforce solutions, these trends pledge to introduce compelling progressions focused on enhancing customer contentment and optimizing business functions.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/11_KaHIe6a8n.jpg?updatedAt=1714998992366', 3, '6 Call Center Trends for Better Customer Experience in 2024', '2024 is the year to proactively revolutionize your customer experience strategy with these call center trends to drive success in this competitive environment.', 'call centre jobs, career opportunities, high paying jobs', 8, '2024-03-11', '2024-05-06 10:54:47', NULL),
(12, 4, 'Elevating Employee Training & Development with Modern Tech Solutions', 'employee-training-and-development', 'In today\'s fast-paced business landscape, employee training and development have become critical pillars for organizational growth and competitiveness. In recent years, technological innovations have reshaped how companies approach training programs.', 'Here, we explore how integrating technology in training and development can significantly enhance employees\' learning experience while providing valuable insights into state-of-the-art solutions.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/12_zd2-K8SEEJ.jpg?updatedAt=1714998988897', 3, 'Elevating Employee Training With Modern Tech Solutions', 'Learn the benefits of implementing tech in employee training methods. From LMS to VR, find out how modern tech will help you grow in the corporate world.', 'employee training and development', 7, '2024-03-12', '2024-05-06 10:56:32', NULL),
(13, 4, 'The Role of Customer Data Analysis in Digital Marketing', 'customer-data-analysis', 'The divide between online content consumption and consumer behavior is closing quickly in the rapidly changing digital market. As a result, conventional market research is transitioning into advanced customer data analysis.', 'While more businesses are embracing this method to tailor campaigns and predict consumer requirements, numerous encounter hurdles in optimizing its advantages. This article informs them about a plan for efficiently utilizing customer data, enhancing marketing tactics, and remaining adaptable in a dynamic digital landscape.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/13_04071CaYWH.jpg?updatedAt=1714998985101', 3, 'The Future of Digital Marketing: Customer Data Analysis', 'Explore the future of digital marketing through customer data analysis. Stay ahead with insights on leveraging data for effective strategies.', 'customer data analysis, digital marketing', 6, '2024-03-13', '2024-05-06 10:58:24', NULL),
(14, 5, 'Elevating Modern Spaces: The Blend of Luxury and Smart Technology', 'smarter-luxurious-solutions-for-businesses-and-homes', 'In today\'s fast-paced world, integrating smart technology into our homes and businesses isn\'t just about keeping up with trends—it\'s about redefining the essence of convenience, sustainability, and security. This evolution towards more intelligent living and working environments embodies the perfect blend between luxury and efficiency, offering solutions that cater to a modern lifestyle that is as demanding as sophisticated.\r\n', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/14_Y9h-2Rh96F.jpg?updatedAt=1714998986300', 2, 'Elevating Spaces: Smart Solutions for Homes and Businesses', 'Simplify your businesses and elevate your homes! Learn how integrating smart technology solutions can create luxurious and convenient spaces for you.', 'smart solutions, luxurious solution, business aesthetic, business interior, home interior, interior', 5, '2024-03-14', '2024-05-06 11:00:08', NULL),
(15, 1, 'Top Sales Software & Penetration Testing Services in India', 'best-sales-software-penetration-testing-services', 'Mastering e-commerce and protecting your software from cyber threats is vital in today\'s digital era. Sales professionals, software engineers, and IT administrators always create new strategies to enhance productivity and fortify digital spaces. ', 'In today\'s competitive market, staying ahead and ensuring security requires a deep comprehension of cutting-edge sales tools and the significance of penetration testing solutions.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/15_OdMwh58epa.jpg?updatedAt=1714998967219', 2, 'Top Sales Software & Penetration Testing Services in 2024 ', 'These are the top sales software and penetration testing services. 1. HubSpot Sales 2. Slack 3. Outreach 4. Metasploit 5. Nessus 6. Leadfeeder and more.', 'sales software, penetration testing services', 2, '2024-03-15', '2024-05-06 12:23:15', NULL),
(16, 4, 'Revolutionizing Industries: Advances in Healthcare, Real Estate, and Manufacturing', 'revolution-in-healthcare-real-estate-manufacturing', 'In today\'s tech-driven world, innovation is like the spark igniting change across healthcare, real estate, and manufacturing sectors. The evolution of tech is reshaping how things work, bringing new possibilities that could shape our future. This blog explores the basics of this transformation, highlighting breakthroughs in different fields, collaborations between industries, efforts towards sustainability, and the challenges ahead.\r\n', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/16_hxlrOSXrnm.jpg?updatedAt=1714998983011', 2, 'Revolution in Healthcare, Real Estate & Manufacturing', 'Know more about the advances made in the healthcare, real estate, and manufacturing industries and learn how these advances are transforming how we live.', 'healthcare, real estate, manufacturing', 6, '2024-03-16', '2024-05-06 12:25:08', NULL),
(17, 4, 'Navigating Modern Challenges: Strategies to Thrive in Business and Technology', 'strategies-for-success-in-business-and-technology', 'Companies face challenges in today\'s fast-paced world, where business and technology are more intertwined than ever. These range from digital transformation to keeping up in a competitive environment. Yet, with the right approach, businesses can transform these hurdles into chances for growth and innovation', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/17_Ja7yGOYrX-.jpg?updatedAt=1714998986440', 2, 'Success Strategies for Today\'s Business & Tech Challenges', 'Discover success strategies in business & technology. Address modern challenges & apply these strategies for victory in navigating the business path.', 'tech challenges, business challenges, tech in business', 1, '2024-03-17', '2024-05-06 12:26:52', NULL),
(18, 4, 'Driving Efficiency: Know The Impact of Industrial Machines', 'industrial-machines-enhance-work-efficiency', 'India\'s swiftly evolving industrial sector, particularly in manufacturing and associated fields, is undergoing notable changes. Central to this transformation is the pivotal function of industrial machinery in propelling advancements.', 'Industrial machinery has revolutionized manufacturing procedures, significantly boosting efficiency and output. This article discusses the profound influence of these machines on the prospects of diverse sectors in India, enhancing operational efficiency and fostering business expansion.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/18_g6v9-TbEx.jpg?updatedAt=1714998916051', 2, 'Industrial Machines: Revolutionizing Efficiency Across India', 'Gain insights into how industrial machines streamline operations and boost output across various sectors in India.', 'industrial machines in India', 4, '2024-03-18', '2024-05-06 12:28:25', NULL),
(19, 7, 'Office Cleaning Jobs at $43/HR | No Experience Required', 'office-cleaning-jobs-with-no-prior-experience', 'In the current economic landscape, finding a job that offers a good pay package without demanding extensive experience upfront can be a formidable challenge. However, the realm of office cleaning jobs stands out as a beacon of hope for those new to the workforce or considering a career transition. This guide highlights how securing a role in office cleaning can be accessible and financially rewarding, with potential earnings of up to $43 per hour, even for beginners in the field.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/19_EC_BFmR2G.jpg?updatedAt=1714998984352', 3, ' Earn $43/HR in Office Cleaning Jobs | No Experience Required', 'Are you looking for lucrative job opportunities? Office cleaning jobs offer up to $43/hr, flexible working hours, no age limits, and a chance for career growth!', 'jobs without experience, high paying jobs', 3, '2024-03-19', '2024-05-06 12:29:33', NULL),
(20, 7, '$51/hr Jobs For Circuit Board Assembly: Entry-Level | Both Gender |', 'jobs-for-circuit-board-assembly', 'In today\'s job market, finding opportunities that offer substantial income without requiring years of experience can feel very exhausting. Yet, the increasingly vital tech industry is breaking molds and setting new standards, especially within manufacturing and engineering. ', 'Specifically, circuit board assembler positions are emerging as highly lucrative roles, enticing job seekers with competitive wages, entry-level accessibility, and promising paths for career progression.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/20_iSoIuPUd9.jpg?updatedAt=1714998914327', 2, '$51/Hr Zero Experience Jobs For Circuit Board Assembly', 'Explore high-paying, entry-level circuit board assembly jobs offering $51/hr, with training. Gender-inclusive roles with paths for career growth in tech.', 'jobs without experience, high paying jobs', 6, '2024-03-20', '2024-05-06 12:30:44', NULL),
(21, 5, '2-Bedroom Apartments At Prime Location | Affordable Homes at Just $350/Month', 'two-bedroom-apartments-at-prime-location', 'Seeking a two-bedroom apartment centrally located that blends luxury and affordability? Look no further. For just $350 per month, you can secure a spacious and luxurious apartment right in the city\'s heart, ensuring everything you need is just minutes away.', 'Prime location apartments not only promise a prestigious address but also a lifestyle that\'s rich in amenities and conveniences. They are the perfect solution for those who value a mix of style, space, and accessibility.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/21_JUXhcfjHhf.jpg?updatedAt=1714998909801', 3, 'Lux 2-Bedroom Apartments at $350/Month in Prime Locations', 'Prime location apartments are now available at just $350/month. Enjoy luxury, convenience, and affordability in the heart of the city! ', 'apartment at prime location, two bedroom apartment', 2, '2024-03-21', '2024-05-06 12:32:00', NULL),
(22, 7, 'Earn Big with $51/HR Home Care Jobs – No Experience Required', 'hiring-for-home-care-jobs-with-no-experience-needed', 'Today is an era of uncertainties and rapid transformations, and individuals on the job hunt often aspire to a profession that promises stability, satisfaction, and a competitive income. Home care roles emerge as a promising opportunity, providing the chance to significantly impact the lives of others while ensuring financial security, even for those without experience.', 'Both men and women are discovering fulfilling career paths within the expanding home care industry. These professionals are vital in offering support and companionship to individuals requiring assistance with their everyday activities.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/22_mQRSH7ixi7.jpg?updatedAt=1714998907775', 3, 'Home Care Jobs: $51/HR Without Prior Experience', 'Earn big with these Home Care Jobs, which offer $51 per hour for males and females without prior experience. Don\'t miss this well-paid opportunity.', 'home care jobs, jobs without experience, high paying jobs', 8, '2024-03-22', '2024-05-06 12:33:12', NULL),
(23, 7, 'Earn $51/HR with Warehouse Packing Jobs | No Experience Required', 'warehouse-packing-jobs', 'In today\'s job market, finding a good opportunity can seem daunting. Now, picture discovering an exceptional opportunity – a warehouse packing position that pays an impressive $51 per hour without any experience required. This opportunity is more than just a job; it\'s a gateway to a better living standard, available to all applicants regardless of gender. It offers financial stability and represents progress in breaking down conventional gender roles in the workforce.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/23_08QPdPwWT.jpg?updatedAt=1714998899172', 3, '$51/HR | Warehouse Packing Jobs | No Experience Needed', 'Earn $51/hr with warehouse packing jobs! These jobs require no prior experience. Read the blog to know why a warehouse job is your golden opportunity!', 'jobs without experience, high paying jobs', 1, '2024-03-23', '2024-05-06 12:34:29', NULL),
(24, 1, 'Tablets That Offers Medicare: An Essential Guide for Seniors', 'medical-healthcare-for-seniors', 'In today\'s digital age, staying connected, informed, and healthy has never been more important—especially for seniors. Medicare\'s offering of tablets makes it easier for seniors to access healthcare services, manage medication, and keep in touch with loved ones. With a special offer available for the next 24 hours, it\'s time to understand how you can make the most of this opportunity.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/24_Xdas__JxWe.jpg?updatedAt=1714998894708', 2, 'Digital Tablets That Offer Medical Guidance For Seniors', 'These tech-savvy tablets offer medical care guidance for seniors. Check out their benefits, how these tablets help seniors, and which devices offers it.', 'tablets, health, medical tablets', 3, '2024-03-24', '2024-05-06 12:35:38', NULL),
(25, 5, 'No Credit Score Needed: Explore Cashback Credit Card Options', 'cash-back-credit-cards-without-credit-score-restrictions', 'In today\'s economic requirements, where saving is equivalent to earning, cashback credit cards have become indispensable for millennials and young professionals seeking to support their income and make informed financial choices.', 'Traditional credit cards are increasingly overshadowed by those offering cashback incentives, particularly those with generous credit limits of £7,000 or more and accessibility without stringent credit score requirements. Let\'s learn more about these financial options, highlighting the four best choices.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/25_6kTfZZ2CDE.jpg?updatedAt=1714998910009', 2, 'Top 4 Cashback Credit Cards Offering ₤7K Limit or More ', 'Cashback credit cards provide a £7K limit or more without credit score limitations. 1. Chase Sapphire Preferred Card  2. Discover it Cashback, and more.', 'cashback, cashback on credit card, save money', 5, '2024-03-25', '2024-05-06 12:36:55', NULL),
(26, 5, 'Smartphone: Buy Now, Pay Later - No Credit Check Required', 'buy-smartphone-without-credit-check', 'In today\'s fast-paced world, having a reliable and up-to-date smartphone is not just a luxury—it\'s a necessity. Whether you\'re a tech enthusiast eager to get your hands on the latest gadget, a budget-conscious consumer looking for the best value, or a young adult stepping into independence, there\'s one hurdle many face when upgrading their phone: the financial investment. ', 'Enter the game-changing solution of \"Buy Now, Pay Later\" (BNPL) smartphone plans, designed to make your next upgrade smooth, straightforward, and stress-free. This enticing option opens up possibilities; no credit check is required!', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/26_TAQXlcjiBr.jpg?updatedAt=1714998879908', 2, 'Get the Latest Smartphone Today - Pay Later, No Credit Check', 'Flexible Payment Plans • Simple Application Process • Transparent Pricing. Buy the latest smartphone now and pay later without any credit check required! ', 'Smartphone, Pay Later', 2, '2024-05-07', '2024-05-07 07:28:27', NULL),
(27, 4, 'The Essential Role of Attorneys in Shaping Society', 'exploring-role-and-influence-of-attorneys-in-society', 'Understanding the details of the law requires specialized knowledge and skills that often escape most people. Attorneys provide invaluable contributions in this sphere, serving as advocates and advisors and playing a pivotal role in upholding the justice system\'s integrity. ', 'This blog aims to enlighten the multifaceted role of attorneys and highlight their significance across various aspects of life. Whether seeking personal legal advice, overseeing a small business, or having legal aspirations, their contribution is invaluable.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/27_fY395pg7l8.jpg?updatedAt=1714998896987', 3, 'The Power of Attorneys in Shaping Society', 'Learn about the significant impact of attorneys in shaping society. 1. Functions & Objectives of an Attorney • 2. Qualifications & Experiences and more. ', 'Impact of Attorneys in Society', 3, '2024-05-07', '2024-05-07 07:30:10', NULL),
(28, 3, 'Reasons Why Walk-In Bathtubs Are a Game-Changer for the Elderly ', 'walk-in-bathtubs-for-elderly', 'As we age, our homes need to evolve with us. The bathroom, in particular, requires attention, as it often becomes the room most associated with risk for seniors. Enter walk-in tubs, a solution that’s gaining popularity for its safety features and therapeutic benefits. ', 'This type of bathtub is designed with a door on the side, allowing the user to enter without climbing over the side. But what exactly makes these tubs so beneficial for the elderly?', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/28_dX8JHwQPi.jpg?updatedAt=1714998902127', 3, 'Walk-In Bathtubs Are Becoming A Game-Changer For Elderly', 'Discover how walk-in bathtubs offer a safer, more comfortable bathing solution for seniors, focusing on mobility, hydrotherapy, and a way to age easily.', 'walk in tubs', 3, '2024-05-07', '2024-05-07 07:31:37', NULL),
(29, 5, 'Everything You Need To Understand About Your Home\'s Plumbing System', 'understand-home-plumbing-system', 'Plumbing systems are easily overlooked in the daily rhythm of home life. Yet, they play a pivotal role in ensuring comfort, hygiene, and even the safety of our living spaces.', 'In this post, we\'ll explore the importance of maintaining a healthy plumbing system, its various types, its key functions, and the critical moments when enlisting a professional plumber becomes necessary.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/29_whO5rCt3F.jpg?updatedAt=1714998903562', 2, 'Essential Information About Your Home Plumbing System', 'Master your home plumbing issues with expert advice on proper maintenance and repair and when to seek professional help. This is a must-read for homeowners.', 'Plumbing Systems', 4, '2024-05-07', '2024-05-07 07:33:14', NULL),
