(1, 1, 'Google Cloud Platform: Growing Impact on Businesses in the Digital World', 'what-is-google-cloud-platform', 'The Google Cloud Platform (GCP) has emerged as a crucial aspect in shaping the digital landscape, offering scalable cloud solutions that power everything from enterprise-level businesses to innovative startups. In an era where digital transformation is beneficial and essential for survival and growth, GCP provides robust tools that foster innovation, scalability, and security. This blog covers the complexities of the Google Cloud Platform, highlighting its indispensable role, importance, and impact on today’s digital era.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/1_R63-rrt9Ei.jpg?updatedAt=1714998955590', 3, 'Why Google Cloud Platform is Essential for Your Business', ' Learn about the Google Cloud Platform and how it can help you grow your business with advanced security, scalability, and data-driven insights.', 'Google Cloud Platform, what is Google Cloud platform', 8, '2024-03-01', '2024-05-06 10:28:21', NULL),
(2, 1, 'Top Data Security Tools and Best Practices for Ensuring Your Online Safety', 'data-security-tools-and-practices', 'Securing your data is prudent and necessary in a digital realm filled with cyber threats. For small business owners and IT professionals, understanding the tools and practices that safeguard digital information is critical. This comprehensive guide will help you gain essential knowledge on data security, offering insights into the leading tools and best practices for fortifying your online presence.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/2_inFUeu4wV.jpg?updatedAt=1714998957470', 3, 'Data Security Guide: Top Tools & Practices for Online Safety', 'Learn the top data security tools and practices to protect your online presence. Understand everything from firewalls to encryption and beyond.', 'data security, what is data security, data security tools, data security practices', 1, '2024-03-02', '2024-05-06 10:30:32', NULL),
(3, 2, 'Explore India\'s Top 5 Business Management Degree Programs', '5-best-business-management-degree-programs', 'India\'s robust economic growth over the past few decades has created a crucial need for skilled business professionals. In response, numerous educational institutions have emerged, offering specialized business management degree programs to cater to this escalating demand.', 'Discover the top 5 business management degree programs in India that students and employers highly value. They aim to equip aspiring individuals with the necessary knowledge and skills to thrive in the constantly changing business environment.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/3_-UD2brbJ50.jpg?updatedAt=1714998963915', 2, 'India\'s Best 5 Business Management Degree Programs for 2024', 'Know India\'s top 5 business management degree programs for 2024. 1. Indian Institute of Management (IIM) • 2. Xavier School of Management (XLRI) and more.', 'Business Management Degree, Degree Programs, Degree Programs in India for 2024, Management Degree, Business Management', 7, '2024-03-03', '2024-05-06 10:32:25', NULL),
(4, 2, 'The Future of Digital Marketing: Courses You Can\'t-Miss in 2024', 'digital-marketing-courses-for-beginners', 'In an age where technology constantly transforms our ways of connecting and doing business, staying at the forefront of digital marketing is more important than ever. The digital marketing world of 2024 is set to introduce both new challenges and opportunities for marketers keen to establish their presence. ', 'No matter if you\'re a newcomer eager to enter this dynamic field or an experienced professional looking to enhance your digital expertise, the right training can pave the way to success. Here\'s a look ahead at the future of digital marketing through the essential courses aimed at boosting your skills.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/4_ltfFvOx9ta.jpg?updatedAt=1714998961905', 2, 'Top Digital Marketing Courses You Cannot Miss in 2024', 'Digital Marketing is one of the fastest-growing sectors in 2024. Dive into the field and upskill yourself with these popular digital marketing courses today!', 'digital marketing courses, digital marketing, digital marketing course', 2, '2024-03-05', '2024-05-06 10:34:29', NULL),
(5, 2, 'Consider These 5 Best Animation Courses in India for 2024', 'best-animation-courses', 'Animation is an ever-evolving and captivating domain that attracts individuals with creative flair and technological aptitude, all driven by a passion for storytelling. With its emerging entertainment industry and internationally acclaimed IT sector, India has become a prominent destination for animation education, fostering talent and driving innovation in this dynamic field.', 'As advanced technologies and digital platforms continue to rise, the demand for proficient animators in India has surged, emphasizing the importance of selecting the appropriate educational route. Let\'s explore some of India\'s top animation courses tailored for 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/5_-oG4ojtENH.jpg?updatedAt=1714998958318', 2, 'Explore the 5 Best Animation Courses in India for 2024', 'These are India\'s 5 best animation courses for 2024. 1. National Institute of Design (NID) • 2. Industrial Design Centre (IDC), IIT Bombay & more.', 'animation courses ,  National Institute of Design, NID, WWI, Industrial Design Centre, IDC', 6, '2024-03-05', '2024-05-06 10:37:48', NULL),
(6, 3, 'A Complete Guide to Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, and How to Prevent', 'cataract-surgery', 'Cataracts are a principal cause of vision impairment worldwide, affecting millions yearly. However, a comprehensive understanding of cataracts can significantly empower individuals, enabling them to proactively approach their visual health. ', 'We’ll unravel the mystery of cataracts, discover their common causes and symptoms, and discuss the crucial steps one can take toward their prevention. By gaining a deeper insight into these aspects, you can make informed decisions regarding your sight health and potentially minimize the impact of cataracts on your life.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/6_6ge1BFlfD-.jpg?updatedAt=1714998963843', 2, 'Everything About Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, Prevention', 'Are you facing cataracts? Read our guide on symptom recognition, when to opt for surgery, and post-surgery care for a smooth recovery and better eye health.', 'cataract surgery, cataract awareness, cataract causes, cataract symptoms, cataract prevention', 3, '2024-03-06', '2024-05-06 10:39:36', NULL),
(7, 4, 'Find Out the Benefits of Coworking Spaces for Digital Nomads', 'benefits-of-coworking-spaces-for-digital-nomads', 'In the past decade, coworking spaces have become increasingly popular, mirroring the growth of digital nomadism and remote work trends. These spaces function as collaborative hubs, resembling communal offices, and cater to freelancers, entrepreneurs, and startups alike. This blog analyzes the diverse advantages of coworking spaces, which are exceptionally appealing to digital nomads seeking flexibility while maintaining a professional environment.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/7_ROoYi4eEpG.jpg?updatedAt=1714998964737', 2, 'The Essential Benefits of Coworking Spaces for Digital Nomads', 'Explore the benefits that coworking spaces offer digital nomads, from stimulating creativity and innovation to encouraging a healthy work-life balance.', 'coworking spaces, spaces for modern business, digital nomads, advantages of coworking spaces', 5, '2024-03-07', '2024-05-06 10:41:48', NULL),
(8, 1, 'Stay Informed About These Cybersecurity Trends in 2024', 'key-cybersecurity-trends-for-2024', 'In our swiftly changing digital realm, the significance of cybersecurity is experiencing exponential growth. With technological advancements occurring at a blistering pace, businesses, IT professionals, and the general public must stay vigilant about cybersecurity trends. In 2024, significant shifts and challenges emerged, especially with the rise of Generative AI, Quantum Computing, and more sophisticated cybersecurity threats.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/8_VYNGgunmf.jpg?updatedAt=1714998961472', 3, 'Stay Informed About the Key Cybersecurity Trends for 2024', 'Discover the critical cybersecurity trends for 2024. 1. Artificial Intelligence (AI) & Machine Learning (ML) • 2. Internet of Things (IoT) Security, and more. ', 'cyber crimes, cybersecurity experts, cybersecurity degree, cybersecurity education', 4, '2024-03-08', '2024-05-06 10:44:11', NULL),
(9, 5, 'Home Security Cameras: How to Pick the Right One for Your Safety Needs', 'how-to-choose-the-right-home-security-system', 'Today, keeping our homes and loved ones safe is more important than ever, which means maintaining the proper security measures. Security cameras are vital for protecting our areas, but picking the best one with many options can take time.', 'Our guide makes it easy, giving you all the info you need to choose the right security camera system for your home. We\'ll help you figure out what you need and show you the newest features and tech in surveillance.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/answerlocate/9_jX8HgBWu4.jpg?updatedAt=1714998990861', 1, 'Looking for the best security camera for your home? From identifying your needs to understanding technical features, we\'ll help you make the right choice.', 'Looking for the best security camera for your home? From identifying your needs to understanding technical features, we\'ll help you make the right choice.', 'security camera for home, security camera system, safety', 4, '2024-03-09', '2024-05-06 10:50:34', NULL),
